                    <br />
                    Draconicon is the best tabletop gaming convention in Israel, dedicated to boardgames, RPG's, Miniatures, Card games, LARP's and more. It has more than a hundred events, an exhibition hall, free play areas, free to use games library, seminars and more... Come and play!
