                        Events at the Convention
                    </h3>
                    <p class="card-paragraph">
                        We have over a hundred different events going on. The events will be published on our site during July, in our games page. There is also a free-to-play area as well as a free games library. If you are unable to read Hebrew and need help finding a game, just ask us and we will gladly help!
