                    </h3>
                    <p class="card-paragraph">
                        Enjoy our exhibition hall, which hosts all the leading Israeli gaming companies and stores as well as indie games, accessories and art stands. There is also a 2nd-hand stand where you can buy and sell used games and give a new life to an old game.
