            <div class="card card-gray-float">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title text-bold">
                        <i class="fa fa-fw fa-dragon dragon-organge-color"></i>
                        &nbsp;
                        Language Note
                    </h3>
                    <p class="card-paragraph">
                        We are happy to accommodate english-only speaking gamers, so you are welcome to come and join us for two days of gaming fun in the heart of Tel-Aviv!
                        Most Israeli gamers have good english, and we have had a large number of English-only speaking players join us and enjoy the convention. Since only a handful of RPG's and boardgames have been translated to Hebrew, most of the games themselves in the conventions are in English.
                        If you need more information about Draconicon, the other parts of the website are in hebrew - you can either use Google Translate or contact us.
